document.discussion_title: Southbound I-35 upper deck reopened after power lines repaired
document.topic_text: Southbound I-35 upper deck reopened after power lines repaired American-Statesman Monday 25th April, 2016 Both the northbound and southbound lanes of Interstate 35's upper deck have reopened for traffic after road crews repaired power lines in the area, construction crews say.Police said a private company was trying to lay some cables and ran into problems earlier this morning, leading to complaints about traffic on social media.The sheriff's office said they had to close the lanes to allow crews to stretch cable across the highway....
